{"tid":1242240,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"主流意見已經被和理非控制 等輸","createTime":"2019-06-19T03:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T03:48:02.000Z","uid":167878,"like":3,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"72973e6d0f92cc24fa0d842b8404b24a6a456e61","tid":1242240,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:40:19.000Z","msg":"本來今次令政府暫緩就係612理勇武派<br />\n警方使用暴力鎮壓 有勁多外國媒體關注<br />\n係勇武派既勝利 我仲好期勇武掘起<br />\n<br />\n點知又比大台騎劫咗 係咁叫人616唔好衝<br />\n616出咗200萬人 換嚟既只有林鄭道歉<br />\n無行動升級 你諗下如果嗰200萬人有一成<br />\n去衝立法會 禮賓府 林鄭仲敢當我地無到?<br />\n<br />\n咁快就叫人等選舉 話乜野唔使急 等多陣<br />\n到今時今日班柒頭仲諗跟人規矩玩<br />\n對上次雨革隔咗成五年 不進反退啊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無外國勢力幫手 你唔好諗住會實現到普選<br />\n如果真係想要普選 唯一方法繼續衝 大力衝<br />\n衝到中國出解放軍 外國有理由出手</span>"},{"pid":"35a48c2fa6ddd61804e58d6dd6afd69c848dc8d4","tid":1242240,"uid":167878,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:41:00.000Z","msg":"屌柒你地班和理非啊"},{"pid":"b94b95fb17482918380305edb162c706b55d8206","tid":1242240,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:41:30.000Z","msg":"係咪第一日留意政治啊"},{"pid":"fad97d9c441072622afa9b94f5466a38eeb7fe40","tid":1242240,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:41:47.000Z","msg":"選舉你老味"},{"pid":"894d92ee065ec9d9d31681bd42ef46084bfa5958","tid":1242240,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:41:58.000Z","msg":"選咗咁撚多年"},{"pid":"a67249017d7efaefee6a94623511b14f848b601e","tid":1242240,"uid":257422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:42:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e65af24053e46346fd8de6c51f8fde87adde08a6","tid":1242240,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:42:29.000Z","msg":"立法會一直只能守 無力攻"},{"pid":"1400657be86d00883e1fb4e100709fd3607cda7d","tid":1242240,"uid":173814,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:42:30.000Z","msg":"分化撚"},{"pid":"8853dd6a9e92b52ab8afe798bfa032c20ceb5d8c","tid":1242240,"uid":175930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"72973e6d0f92cc24fa0d842b8404b24a6a456e6